 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1685/use-conky-on-the-desktop/?answer=1696#post-id-1696</link><description>Of course it's possible. Just configure your Conky as usual, and add `exec --no-startup-id conky` at the end of your `.i3/config` file to launch it at startup.</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2013 14:16:33 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1685/use-conky-on-the-desktop/?answer=1696#post-id-1696</guid></item></channel></rss>